Desert Wind (Stance) [Fire]
Level: Swordsage 3
Prerequisite: One Desert Wind maneuver
Initiation Action: 1 swift action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Stance

The flame from your weapon hangs in midair, providing you with a fiery defense against your attackers. An adjacent opponent that hits you with a melee attack while you are in this stance takes 5 points of fire damage.

This stance is a supernatural ability.
